productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Isabela has one of these. She works as a taxidermist and she says it looks monochromatic.
My goldfinch loves to play with it.
one of my hobbies is antique-shopping. and when i'm antique-shopping this works great.
heard about this on powerviolence radio, decided to give it a try.
I saw one of these in South Korea and I bought one.
